title: Masked (2012) (Alice)
description: Injured during a mission in the Caucasus, Sergeant Frank Braffort returns to Paris after six years of absence. What he finds is Paris-Metropolis, a city changed under the rule of Prefect Beauregard where gigantic retro-futuristic is all the rage and mysterious anomalies are on the rise. A city that will take Braffort and link their destinies forever...
